<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>国土报最新头条</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 20 Nov 2023 20:08:00 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>议会中关于人质的令人作呕的辩论让哈马斯的叶海亚辛瓦尔微笑</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-20/ty-article/.premium/a-sickening-debate-in-the-knesset-on-hostages-makes-hamas-yahya-sinwar-smile/0000018b-ee25-d36e-a3cb-fe779ec00000</link><description>在这一天，以色列国家耻辱部部长伊塔马尔·本·格维尔（Itamar Ben-Gvir）突然提出了一项对恐怖分子判处死刑的法案。到现在为止，他都聪明地在这黑暗的日子里保持沉默。</description><pubDate>Mon, 20 Nov 2023 19:59:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-20/ty-article/.premium/a-sickening-debate-in-the-knesset-on-hostages-makes-hamas-yahya-sinwar-smile/0000018b-ee25-d36e-a3cb-fe779ec00000</guid></item><item><title>调查显示，超过一半的犹太学生在美国大学校园感到害怕</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-11-20/ty-article/.premium/more-than-half-of-jewish-students-feel-scared-on-u-s-college-campuses-survey-shows/0000018b-ede0-d4f0-affb-efe341bb0000</link><description>这项针对 300 名犹太学生进行的在线调查还发现，超过四分之一的人因为自己是犹太人或因为对以色列的看法而在校园里感到不受欢迎。</description><pubDate>Mon, 20 Nov 2023 18:32:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-11-20/ty-article/.premium/more-than-half-of-jewish-students-feel-scared-on-u-s-college-campuses-survey-shows/0000018b-ede0-d4f0-affb-efe341bb0000</guid></item><item><title>“羞辱是这场战争最残酷的经历之一”：恐惧和屈服笼罩着加沙人向南逃亡的道路</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-20/ty-article-magazine/.premium/fear-and-submission-reign-in-the-path-of-gazans-fleeing-south/0000018b-ed28-d26b-a18f-efba74320000</link><description>数千人按照以色列国防军的命令从加沙城向南逃亡，他们在街道上遇到了被摧毁的建筑物和死亡，但在以色列国防军检查站，人们的恐惧最为严重。联合国：以色列国防军似乎正在运行面部识别系统</description><pubDate>Mon, 20 Nov 2023 18:30:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-20/ty-article-magazine/.premium/fear-and-submission-reign-in-the-path-of-gazans-fleeing-south/0000018b-ed28-d26b-a18f-efba74320000</guid></item><item><title>以色列贝都因人称，他在拘留期间因在社交媒体上发布帖子而遭到警卫殴打</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-20/ty-article/.premium/israeli-bedouin-says-guards-severely-beat-him-during-detention-over-social-media-posts/0000018b-ebfc-d8b1-a9df-ebff14980000</link><description>海塔姆·胡瓦什拉 (Haitam Huwashla) 因 Facebook 帖子声称对哈马斯表示同情而被捕，并在没有受到指控的情况下被释放，他表示他的帖子完全被误解，而拘留后的 X 光检查显示肋骨破裂和椎间盘突出</description><pubDate>Mon, 20 Nov 2023 18:17:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-20/ty-article/.premium/israeli-bedouin-says-guards-severely-beat-him-during-detention-over-social-media-posts/0000018b-ebfc-d8b1-a9df-ebff14980000</guid></item><item><title>女兵警告哈马斯即将发动袭击，但遭到忽视</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-20/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-women-soldiers-who-warned-of-a-pending-hamas-attack-and-were-ignored/0000018b-ed76-d4f0-affb-eff740150000</link><description>在过去的一年里，驻扎在加沙边境的以色列国防军观察员（全部是女性）警告说，正在发生一些不寻常的事情。 10 月 7 日大屠杀的幸存者相信，如果是男人发出警报，今天的情况会有所不同</description><pubDate>Mon, 20 Nov 2023 17:47:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-20/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-women-soldiers-who-warned-of-a-pending-hamas-attack-and-were-ignored/0000018b-ed76-d4f0-affb-eff740150000</guid></item><item><title>美国敦促以色列允许加沙海上天然气储备以重振巴勒斯坦经济</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-20/ty-article/.premium/u-s-to-push-israel-to-allow-gaza-offshore-gas-reserves-to-revitalize-palestinian-economy/0000018b-ed90-ddc3-afdb-fdd1ff250000</link><description>六月，以色列初步批准了加沙沿岸天然气田的开发。拜登总统的能源安全顾问阿莫斯·霍赫斯坦目前正在访问以色列，他说：“我们不应该夸大其潜力，但它绝对可以成为巴勒斯坦政府的收入来源。”</description><pubDate>Mon, 20 Nov 2023 17:21:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-20/ty-article/.premium/u-s-to-push-israel-to-allow-gaza-offshore-gas-reserves-to-revitalize-palestinian-economy/0000018b-ed90-ddc3-afdb-fdd1ff250000</guid></item><item><title>“可耻”：德语媒体批评德国总理肖尔茨在柏林接待埃尔多安</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2023-11-20/ty-article/.premium/shameful-german-language-press-critical-of-chancellor-scholz-hosting-erdogan-in-berlin/0000018b-ed6b-d26b-a18f-effb63f90000</link><description>德国、奥地利和瑞士媒体强烈谴责土耳其总统的访问，土耳其总统最近将哈马斯描述为“解放组织”</description><pubDate>Mon, 20 Nov 2023 16:26:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2023-11-20/ty-article/.premium/shameful-german-language-press-critical-of-chancellor-scholz-hosting-erdogan-in-berlin/0000018b-ed6b-d26b-a18f-effb63f90000</guid></item><item><title>“深造”的以色列国防军士兵和欺骗性网站：复杂的俄罗斯行动推动加沙虚假信息</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-20/ty-article/.premium/deep-faked-soldiers-and-spoofed-websites-russian-campaign-pushes-gaza-disinformation/0000018b-ed5c-d36e-a3cb-fd5fadd90000</link><description>从外国演员在巴黎绘制并在 Telegram 上分享的大卫之星照片，到各种语言的假新闻故事，克里姆林宫掌控的“分身”运动正在利用以色列与哈马斯的战争来煽动混乱</description><pubDate>Mon, 20 Nov 2023 16:20:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-20/ty-article/.premium/deep-faked-soldiers-and-spoofed-websites-russian-campaign-pushes-gaza-disinformation/0000018b-ed5c-d36e-a3cb-fd5fadd90000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队公布了在加沙地面行动中丧生的另外三名士兵的姓名</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-20/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-releases-names-of-three-additional-soldiers-killed-in-gaza-ground-operation/0000018b-ed28-d4f0-affb-efeb9b140000</link><description>这三人是在过去 24 小时内坠落的，他们被确认为伞兵中士。伊农·塔米尔和参谋中士。 Dvir Barazani 和 Givati 特种作战部队成员参谋军士。埃坦·迪尚</description><pubDate>Mon, 20 Nov 2023 15:28:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-20/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-releases-names-of-three-additional-soldiers-killed-in-gaza-ground-operation/0000018b-ed28-d4f0-affb-efeb9b140000</guid></item><item><title>拜登“重振”巴勒斯坦权力机构的愿景不足以确保加沙的未来</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2023-11-20/ty-article/.premium/bidens-vision-of-a-revitalized-pa-isnt-enough-to-secure-gazas-future/0000018b-ebdc-d6b8-a5ab-effe47300000</link><description>美国总统希望看到约旦河西岸和加沙地带建立一个统一的巴勒斯坦政府，有朝一日可能实现两国解决方案。但他在这一点上与内塔尼亚胡存在严重分歧，如果拜登从言语转向行动，分歧可能会加深</description><pubDate>Mon, 20 Nov 2023 15:02:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2023-11-20/ty-article/.premium/bidens-vision-of-a-revitalized-pa-isnt-enough-to-secure-gazas-future/0000018b-ebdc-d6b8-a5ab-effe47300000</guid></item><item><title>以色列为忽视以色列国防军观察员付出了代价，这个以女性为主的单位在 10 月 7 日遭受重创</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/editorial/2023-11-20/ty-article/israel-pays-the-price-for-neglecting-idf-spotters/0000018b-eccb-d6b8-a5ab-ecebcf630000</link><description></description><pubDate>Mon, 20 Nov 2023 14:28:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/editorial/2023-11-20/ty-article/israel-pays-the-price-for-neglecting-idf-spotters/0000018b-eccb-d6b8-a5ab-ecebcf630000</guid></item><item><title>以色列劫持哈马斯网站，将其变成 10 月 7 日暴行的展示</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-20/ty-article/.premium/israelis-hijack-hamas-com-turning-it-into-a-display-of-october-7-atrocities/0000018b-eca2-d8b1-a9df-ecef8b380000</link><description>该网站上的一个柜台自豪地宣称 1,400 名“犹太复国主义平民被谋杀”，41 名“犹太复国主义儿童和婴儿被谋杀和活活烧死”。该网站似乎没有链接到哈马斯，其实际网站 Hamas.ps 目前似乎处于离线状态</description><pubDate>Mon, 20 Nov 2023 13:32:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-20/ty-article/.premium/israelis-hijack-hamas-com-turning-it-into-a-display-of-october-7-atrocities/0000018b-eca2-d8b1-a9df-ecef8b380000</guid></item><item><title>随着战争的激烈，以色列定居者和士兵试图阻止巴勒斯坦橄榄收获</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-20/ty-article-magazine/.premium/as-war-rages-israeli-settlers-and-soldiers-try-to-block-the-palestinian-olive-harvest/0000018b-ec28-d36e-a3cb-fc7ffc280000</link><description>随着针对巴勒斯坦农民的暴力行为在这方面加剧，像贝扎莱尔·斯莫特里奇这样的极右翼政客已与西岸定居者联手参与竞选活动</description><pubDate>Mon, 20 Nov 2023 13:02:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-20/ty-article-magazine/.premium/as-war-rages-israeli-settlers-and-soldiers-try-to-block-the-palestinian-olive-harvest/0000018b-ec28-d36e-a3cb-fc7ffc280000</guid></item><item><title>过去的人质危机告诉我们以色列人质的未来</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-20/ty-article-magazine/.premium/what-hostage-crises-of-the-past-teach-us-about-israeli-hostages-future/0000018b-ec4c-d32d-abdb-ee4fcb980000</link><description>几十年来，以色列拒绝就释放人质进行谈判。这种情况在 20 世纪 80 年代发生了变化，随后遭到绑架的以色列人家属发起了大规模的公众压力。但这正中巴勒斯坦恐怖组织的下怀吗？连专家也不同意</description><pubDate>Mon, 20 Nov 2023 12:00:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-20/ty-article-magazine/.premium/what-hostage-crises-of-the-past-teach-us-about-israeli-hostages-future/0000018b-ec4c-d32d-abdb-ee4fcb980000</guid></item><item><title>国际奥斯维辛委员会要求“立即无条件”释放人质</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/jewish/2023-11-20/ty-article/.premium/international-auschwitz-council-demands-immediate-and-unconditional-release-of-hostages/0000018b-ec5e-d36e-a3cb-fc5fe9d40000</link><description>国际奥斯维辛委员会对以色列表示“坚定不移的声援”，并呼吁“立即无条件释放”人质，以此作为“制止可怕的死亡螺旋的重要第一步”</description><pubDate>Mon, 20 Nov 2023 11:41:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/jewish/2023-11-20/ty-article/.premium/international-auschwitz-council-demands-immediate-and-unconditional-release-of-hostages/0000018b-ec5e-d36e-a3cb-fc5fe9d40000</guid></item><item><title>“谈论生命，而不是死亡”：以色列人质家属恳求政府放弃恐怖分子死刑</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-20/ty-article/.premium/talk-life-not-death-israeli-hostage-families-beg-govt-to-drop-terrorist-death-penalty/0000018b-ec3c-d6b8-a5ab-ec7e96300000</link><description>尽管哈马斯战争期间在加沙被扣为人质的人的家人含泪恳求，内塔尼亚胡的极右翼伙伴仍坚持举行法律辩论</description><pubDate>Mon, 20 Nov 2023 10:41:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-20/ty-article/.premium/talk-life-not-death-israeli-hostage-families-beg-govt-to-drop-terrorist-death-penalty/0000018b-ec3c-d6b8-a5ab-ec7e96300000</guid></item><item><title>悲伤重聚：我们从未想过哈马斯有一天会摧毁我们的基布兹</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-20/ty-article-magazine/.premium/we-were-a-class-of-13-kibbutz-kids-we-never-could-imagine-this-would-happen/0000018b-e7ca-d05f-a5eb-e7ea55580000</link><description>哈马斯 10 月 7 日袭击的后果：我们出生于 1972 年，在后来被哈马斯摧毁的基布兹共同生活后就分道扬镳了。这就是发生在我儿时朋友身上的事</description><pubDate>Mon, 20 Nov 2023 10:32:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-20/ty-article-magazine/.premium/we-were-a-class-of-13-kibbutz-kids-we-never-could-imagine-this-would-happen/0000018b-e7ca-d05f-a5eb-e7ea55580000</guid></item><item><title>随着反犹太主义的加剧，英国犹太人询问他们在英国是否有未来</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-20/ty-article-opinion/.premium/with-antisemitism-spiking-uk-jews-ask-if-they-have-a-future-in-britain/0000018b-e7a1-d963-a1bb-f7fbede00000</link><description>在英国，我们面临着世界上最糟糕的情况：伊斯兰极端主义反犹太主义与对美国批判种族理论和后殖民罪恶感的简单化解释相结合。自哈马斯发动袭击以来，犹太人仇恨情绪高涨 — — 并且缺乏盟友</description><pubDate>Mon, 20 Nov 2023 09:51:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-20/ty-article-opinion/.premium/with-antisemitism-spiking-uk-jews-ask-if-they-have-a-future-in-britain/0000018b-e7a1-d963-a1bb-f7fbede00000</guid></item><item><title>以色列反对党提议修改民族国家法，增加“平等条款”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-20/ty-article/.premium/israeli-opposition-party-proposes-amending-nation-state-law-with-equality-clause/0000018b-ebbf-d6b8-a5ab-efffca0a0000</link><description>虽然利库德集团尚未表示是否愿意支持一项修正案，但它已提出了一项关于德鲁兹人的基本法，可能是为了阻止这样的修正案，因为德鲁兹人士兵在战斗中的死亡再次引发了关于准“德鲁兹人”的争论。民族国家宪法法</description><pubDate>Mon, 20 Nov 2023 09:47:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-20/ty-article/.premium/israeli-opposition-party-proposes-amending-nation-state-law-with-equality-clause/0000018b-ebbf-d6b8-a5ab-efffca0a0000</guid></item><item><title>25 年前，加沙国际机场开业。随后发生了第二次起义</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2023-11-20/ty-article-magazine/.premium/25-years-ago-gaza-intl-airport-opened-then-came-the-second-intifada/0000018b-e6fd-dffa-adef-e6fd35a10000</link><description>美国总统首次登陆加沙，巴勒斯坦国家航空公司飞往中东各国首都，加沙人开始梦想独立。但随后爆发了战斗，该场被轰炸，此后被洗劫并拆除</description><pubDate>Mon, 20 Nov 2023 07:31:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2023-11-20/ty-article-magazine/.premium/25-years-ago-gaza-intl-airport-opened-then-came-the-second-intifada/0000018b-e6fd-dffa-adef-e6fd35a10000</guid></item></channel></rss>